value.0: Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.

This book, bound in human flesh and written in the blood of surface elves, dictates various summoning spells and the dark creatures they bring forth. There is a bookmark in the book, and on the bookmarked page reads:

"... the summoning of the one requires  the tainted black heart of his former, his evil skull, and another of his pure bones. To reform his body these are required, along with the souls of a thousand warriors of the purest evil. Once these have been assembled and the location prepared the Arch Lich's eternal form can be ressurected, following the proper rune symbols....."
